    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方游戏交流群 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >199271874</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《美少女不想让你死》是一款融合策略塔防，类幸存者，自走棋的游戏。游戏有两种方式，一种游戏方式是保护好英雄并且防守敌人一定轮次的进攻，另外一种游戏方式是保护好英雄并主动进攻，直至击败特定的敌人。游戏内有多种资源，可以按照自己喜欢的战术进行分配，升级，制作等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4308280/extras/7fe921a308fee937674d6b46cafdd54e.avif?t=1771985249\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4308280/extras_big/7fe921a308fee937674d6b46cafdd54e.webp?t=1771985249 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4308280/extras/dcc5ddb8260003942546ffa84d3b17ef.avif?t=1771985249\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4308280/extras_big/dcc5ddb8260003942546ffa84d3b17ef.webp?t=1771985249 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《美少女不想让你死》可以招募众多的美少女战士，战斗方式似于炮塔，定点攻击。但是在战斗中可以指挥美少女进行指定位置移动，增加了灵活机动性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4308280/extras/38c09d5433d186c196929f72eeb88ca6.avif?t=1771985249\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4308280/extras_big/38c09d5433d186c196929f72eeb88ca6.webp?t=1771985249 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4308280/extras/65da25cdf26d7f23adc1b6827b59d43e.avif?t=1771985249\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4308280/extras_big/65da25cdf26d7f23adc1b6827b59d43e.webp?t=1771985249 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为主角的你，英雄</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以获得美少女的各种增益效果，一旦你陷入濒死的危机，美少女会将你传送出战场（也就是战斗失败）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >职业系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色有各自的战斗职业，并且拥有二转，三转职业。特殊职业“铁匠”，“炼金术士”，“工程师”能生产各类物品。“军师”，“商人”，“吟游诗人”，“祭司”等职业各有特色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4308280/extras/2b8fcb7650025f044294f40585260c1d.avif?t=1771985249\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4308280/extras_big/2b8fcb7650025f044294f40585260c1d.webp?t=1771985249 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装备系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富多样的装备。套装。传奇装备。传奇套装。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富的技能，大量的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
